About this hotel

Set in a restored traditional Moroccan townhouse, this refined riad is a 9-minute walk from Jemaa el-Fnaa public square, 13 minutes' walk from Koutoubia Mosque and 3 km from Majorelle Garden.

Check-in time: 2:00 PM
Check-out time: 12:00 PM

    Medina

    Hammam bath houses and covered spice and textile souks line the maze of cobblestoned lanes in the Medina, which occupies Marrakesh’s original fortified citadel. At night, Jemaa el-Fna square teems with snake charmers, folk dancers, and street food vendors serving all manner of food. Bahia Palace and Le Jardin Secret are 19th-century complexes open to the public, with ornate courtyards, mosaics, and gardens.

    About this hotel

    Set in a restored traditional Moroccan townhouse, this refined riad is a 9-minute walk from Jemaa el-Fnaa public square, 13 minutes' walk from Koutoubia Mosque and 3 km from Majorelle Garden. …

    Stylish rooms come with Wi-Fi, safes and minifridges; upgraded rooms have couches, and suites feature 4-poster beds. Room service is offered 24/7. There are no TVs.

    Amenities include a casual bar and an elegant restaurant, along with a lounge featuring lanterns and a heated pool. There's a rooftop terrace and a hammam. Massage treatments and breakfast are available.
